Package pollaxmud.entities

A package that contains all the game entities, such as creatures and items.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Backpack
    This is the class for the players Backpack.
    Book
    This class represents a Book, which inherits from the Item class.
    Course
    This class represents a course.
    Creature
    The creature class.
    Item
    This class is used to represent Items, which other classes representing more specific items inherits from.
    Key
    A class which inherits from Item and represents a Key.
    Player
    Class for representing the Player that the person that is playing the game is controlling.
    Question
    A question to be asked by teachers.
    Sphinx
    A class representing a Sphinx, which inherits from the Creature class.
    Teacher
    This class represents a teacher in the game.

Package pollaxmud.entities Description
